column5: And its about time too!  Look at this glorious percipitation!  Steelhead are jumping for joy....   thoughts anyone?
Hip Hip Horay, my well is filling up! Dry since August, with 4 teens in the house!
Send some down here to 'Bama, we need it bad!!!
That glorious rain will be a foot of snow tomorrow........
That is true, and it has caused me to cancel my trip to waterloo for a university tour...but that means that the school has already been told I will be absent, and I can walk to the river!
I never thought I'd say this but I'm acutally glad the tribs are going to be blown, we need it. Rivers should be prime for steel on the weekend!!
God I wish I could be on the river tomorrow.. Browns will be packed in there!
